com.hygenics.crawler

Class GetImages

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hygenics.crawler.GetImages

  • public class GetImages
extends Object
    This class pulls images from a mapping and puts them into a table using the basic jdbcconn (there is only one query needed).If an image requires a cookie, then allow for the images to be grabbed with the individual pages using the appropriate command. An offenderhash and image link are required. The offenderhash is used in the metadata
    Author:
    aevans
